00:51:52.828 --> 00:51:54.927
Gosh. Wait a minute.

805
00:52:10.848 --> 00:52:12.118
Soo Ji.

806
00:52:13.047 --> 00:52:15.918
Ji Ho, do you know what kind of a day I had?

807
00:52:15.918 --> 00:52:18.518
I got off work early today unlike other days,

808
00:52:18.658 --> 00:52:21.558
