00:52:25.527 --> 00:52:29.228
I know. Ho Rang did wrong today.

812
00:52:29.998 --> 00:52:32.868
So stop being mad,

813
00:52:32.967 --> 00:52:36.168
and talk to her face-to-face.

814
00:52:37.038 --> 00:52:38.908
If you leave like this,

815
00:52:39.777 --> 00:52:43.408
Ho Rang will be so lonely today.

816
00:52:44.848 --> 00:52:47.118
Loneliness only comes if you have time.

817
00:52:47.288 --> 00:52:49.817
I'm disappointed in her because she's being hysterical...

818
