00:55:20.067 --> 00:55:22.737
I couldn't talk to them yet. Things got in the way.

846
00:55:28.777 --> 00:55:30.078
By the way,

847
00:55:31.047 --> 00:55:32.918
what do your friends do?

848
00:55:35.018 --> 00:55:36.518
I mean,

849
00:55:38.217 --> 00:55:40.427
what are their jobs and...

